                  <p>Our selection of premium flavoring oils can be used for baking and cooking applications as well as adding to chocolate oils, lip balms and lip gloss oils, candle oils, Scratch-n-Sniff artwork, and candy.</p>
                  <p>Create decadent desserts with extraordinary flavor profiles that any sweet tooth will devour. Add your favorite all-natural flavoring oil to ice cream, cookies, cake, frostings, fudge, chocolate, candy, custards, pies, and more. We have a selection of savory flavoring oils, which are excellent to pair with entrees, side dishes, sauces, soups, and more.</p>
                  <p>These flavor oils are made with all-natural, plant-derived ingredients found in nature. At Nature’s Flavors, our assortment of carefully curated natural flavoring oils includes nearly 1,000 different flavor profiles - some of which are more common, and others are exotic flavor oils that only our expert flavor chemists could create. If you have a specific flavor in mind, let us know, and we can create the custom flavoring oil for you.</p>
